Catching #FOMO because you’re the only one at work without AirPods?🎧 OR enjoy eavesdropping on coworkers but don’t want to be too obvious?🤭 For Day 1 of 5 Days of Giveaways, we are giving away @apple AirPods. Winning is easy!
.
1. Follow @peoplesrevolt.
2. Like + Share this post on your story (don’t forget to tag us so we can keep track)!
3. Tag your friends - the more the better chances at winning ✨
4. Tune in for our IG live on Monday 12/23 at 7:00 P.M central time where we announce all the winners.
.
Contest runs from 12/16-12/22. This contest is not endorsed by Instagram.
